hr.caellian.flow.data

Class Property<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • hr.caellian.flow.data.Property<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type contained by Property object.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Externalizable, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class Property<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Externalizable, java.lang.Cloneable
    Property is data wrapper which makes Flux data manipulation a bit easier and predictable. Custom implementations of Property can handle custom serialization and deserialization or handle certain formats differently.
    Since:
    1.0.0
